Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:04.69,Undead OP-JP ep 13,,0,0,0,,{\fscx85}誰かに盗られる前に ほら {\fscx75}Love is burning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.95,Undead OP-JP ep 13,,0,0,0,,熱を感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:12.13,Undead OP-JP ep 13,,0,0,0,,{\fscx85}ヒリヒリと {\fscx100}刺激的{\fscx75}Romance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.13,Undead OP-JP ep 13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1890, 105)\fs15\fsp-2}Feel it now, feel it now, feel it now
